{
  "stem": "9156.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were very-- and then we became very active in distributing those leaflets against the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We went to the harbor, and I'm-- you know that Hamburg is a harbor and the people who work in the harbors are very significant.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we went there and stood there and handed out those leaflets against the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In the early morning, at 5 o'clock before I went to the university.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We did it in the evening when, for instance, they were always in the dives-- I can only call them-- where they collected.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We went right in there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I remember we always were sure that there was a man and woman together.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And but I still remember that once I lost my partner and a huge-- one of those sailors or whatever they are came next to me and said, you do the right thing, child.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I'll protect you.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he went with me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I was no child, but I was little.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it was incredible, the fight that was put up against the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Not only by the ISK-- the socialists, and the Social Democrats, the unionists.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Lots of them, but I wouldn't know about all of them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But this I know because I was part of it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we thought we can do something, but then '33 comes and Hindenburg-- H-I-N-D-E-N-B-U-R-G-- makes Hitler the Vice Chancellor.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "At that moment they have all the power they need because Hindenburg actually was feeble-minded at that point.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He wasn't quite right there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Then there were other things.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We were in Hamburg.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Hamburg was always more against the Nazis, but Prussia, where Berlin was, they withdrew.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It wasn't that they did everything for the Nazis, but they were-- oh, it won't be so bad.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It's always this.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
